            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/04/%E9%AD%94%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/04/%E9%AD%94%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/",
            "title": "魔改hexo butterfly时遇到的一些问题",
            "date_published": "2023-11-03T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"按照教程设置了文章三栏之后依旧是两栏\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#按照教程设置了文章三栏之后依旧是两栏\">#</a> 按照教程设置了文章三栏之后依旧是两栏</h1>\n<p>我是按照这位大佬的教程设置的：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.fomal.cc/posts/d739261b.html\">https://www.fomal.cc/posts/d739261b.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"解决办法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#解决办法\">#</a> <strong>解决办法</strong></h2>\n<span class='p purple'>可能是之前设置的文章两栏没关</span>\n<ul>\n<li>在网站配置文件_config.yml 找到</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#双侧栏</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">butterfly_article_double_row:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这里把 true 改为 false</p>\n",
